        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 2. Oxysarcodexia digitata sp. nov. (female paratype from Itatiaia, MNRJ). (A-B) ST2-5 and terminalia, ventral view. (C) Spermathecae, lateral view. Abbreviations:ce,cercus;hy, hypoproct;sp,spiracle;ST, sternite;T, tergite;vp, vaginal plate.Scale bars = 0.2 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4615034/files/figure.png" .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4615042>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 4. Oxysarcodexia xon (Dodge),(male specimen from Itatiaia,MNRJ).(A) Epandrium,cercus and surstylus,lateral view.(B) Cercus,posterior view.(C) Phallus and associated structures, lateral view. (D) Phallus ventral view. Abbreviations: ajm, anterior juxtal margin; bp, basiphallus; ce, cercus; dp, distiphallus; j,juxta; ls, lateral stylus;ms, median stylus;po,postgonite;pr,pregonite;su, surstylus;ve, vesica.Scale bars = 0.4 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4615042/files/figure.png" .

